title: ASSISTANT ACCOUNTING CLERK The Union Democrat has an (pic)
text: The Union Democrat has an immediate opening for F/T Assistant in the business office. Responsibilities include daily deposit, newspaper inputting advertising orders, ordering office supplies, posting payments, balancing register and closing office each day and other duties as assigned. Must be detail oriented. Pre-employment drug screening is required. Vacation and sick benefits are available.
